3.3 Security and Cryptography Layer

RabbitOS should separate security responsibilities into multiple components.

Encryption

AES-256-GCM for local storage

TLS 1.3 for networking

Ed25519 for signatures

SHA-256 or SHA-3 for integrity


Homomorphic Encryption

Optional encrypted cloud analytics:

OpenFHE

TenSEAL

Microsoft SEAL


Use cases:

